@startuml
title bindex.json File Creation Workflow

actor User as U
participant "GenAI" as G
participant "Project Information (pom.xml,\nsource files, etc.)" as P
participant "bindex.json" as B
participant "Vector Database" as V

U -> G : Request BINDEX creation
G -> P : Analyze project information using GenAI
P -> G : Return insights

G -> B : Generate bindex.json from project insights
note right of B
- Contains:
  - Content information
  - Metadata for app assembly
end note

B -> V : Store bindex.json in vector database
V -> U : Acknowledge storage
note right of V
Files can be semantically searched
for relevant libraries in the future
end note
@enduml